This application contains a test application with tools for running experiments
similar to positif experiments.

In order to setup an experiment, create an omnetpp.ini file:

	./bin/positifgen.sh <SCENARIO> omnetpp.ini
	WHERE:	<SCENARIO> is one of the scenarios from ./input/scenarios

Run the experiment:

	./locNetwork


This is the directory structure given by: tree -d
.
|-- bin			: tools and scripts
|-- input		: various configuration files
|   |-- ini		: omnetpp '.ini' files
|   `-- scenarios	: positif scenarios
`-- src			: source for tools
